        <li>the layout and design of an OJS journal / series can be individually adapted</li>
        <li>all journal articles are assigned a persistent identifier (DOI), which guarantees permanent searchability</li>
        <li>all journal articles are automatically indexed in RelBib</li>
    </ul>
</p>

